{"name":"Dance Battle","type":"divineGift","img":"icons/magic/control/debuff-energy-snare-purple-blue.webp","data":{"word":"Dance","description":"Commit Effort. While active, your dance becomes terrifying or impossibly seductive to foes, being treated as a magical weapon doing 1d10 emotional damage with a range out to visual distance. Against Mobs, this damage is read straight. If a creature is brought to zero hit points by this damage, it can either be struck dead by the horror or beauty of the dance, be compelled to flee, or be seduced to your service for the rest of the scene. In the latter case, the creature regains 1 hit point and is suicidally obedient to the end of the scene.","constant":false,"instant":false,"onTurn":true,"action":false,"smite":false,"noEffort":false,"atWill":true,"scene":false,"day":false,"greater":true,"combatPower":true},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"9kLb9OnQ3UEYBEz7":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.5LsjEn5FEsdTbcFL"}},"_id":"1VBq3TQ8D2dSbzc1"}
